Office Party
============

"Killer jukeboxing for shared spaces."

Requirements
------------

OS X 10.5
iTunes 7
rails gem 2.0.2
rb-appscript gem 0.5.0

(is that all?)

Usage
-----

rake db:migrate
script/server
switch iTunes to play from party shuffle
make users, rate tracks
iTunes gets updated with average of everyone's ratings


